---
title: Plant-Based Pumpkin Ravioli with Creamy Spinach Sauce & Baby Broccoli
description: Let’s veggie-fy ravioli with this plant-based ravioli packed full of pumpkin and coated in a creamy sauce
seasoned with herbs and spinach. Add a zap of chilli flakes to zest up the baby broccoli and finish with
a punch of flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
